
  jelastic-mercurial - Deploy a mercurial binary tar-ball (tar.gz) to elastx nexus server. 


DESCRIPTION
  jelastic-mercurial version manages a mercurial binary tar-ball (src/main/resources/archive.tar.gz)
  to be used in on jelastic VDS hosts. 

  The git binary tar ball as of now has been built in Jockes VDS environment. 


BUILD DISTRIBUTIONS

  STEPS
  1. Prepare a new mercurial binary from source.
  2. Update the jelastic-mercurial project on build server. 
  3. Release jelastic-mercurial project on any machine to elastx Nexus.
  
  BUILD SERVER
  The build server should be a VDS to ensure the same CentOS version that the git binary
  will work on any other jelastic host. 

